# Forcer HTTPS
http://* https://:splat 301!

# Rediriger le sous-domaine Netlify vers le domaine principal
https://bsinternationala.netlify.app/* https://bsinternationales.com/:splat 301!

# Rediriger www vers non-www
https://www.bsinternationales.com/* https://bsinternationales.com/:splat 301!

# Rediriger les URLs sans .html vers .html
/scholar    /scholar.html    301
/business   /business.html   301
/express    /express.html    301
/about      /about.html      301

# Rediriger la racine vers home.html
/           /home.html       301 